Modal Header Themes

You can insert className on the ".modal-dialog" container, for example:
<div class="modal-dialog modal-primary">...</div>

Available className: modal-primary modal-success modal-info modal-warning modal-danger modal-red modal-orange modal-yellow modal-green modal-black modal-blue modal-violet modal-pink modal-grey
